title: FHS Class of '93 to Mark 25 Years
title_page: FHS Class of '93 to Mark 25 Years
maintext: FITCHBURG -- The Fitchburg High School Class of 1993 will celebrate its 25th Class Reunion on Saturday, Oct. 20, from 7 to 11 p.m., at the Marconi Club, 36 Birch Street Passway. For more details, contact Scott Jarvi at fhs1993 alumni@gmail.com .
